","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event08-05-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"네! 무사도를 추구하는 사무라이처럼 돼야겠다고\n언제나 생각하고 있어요♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event08-05-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"하지만~ 이브 짱은 진짜 사무라이를 본 적 없잖아?\n……뭐, 나도 없긴 하지만.\n그런데 어째서 사무라이를 동경하는 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event08-05-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"음~ ……저는 자신의 의지를 관철하는 강함과 동료를 위한 마음,\n그런 것을 소중하게 여기는 무사도에 매력을 느꼈어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event08-05-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"그리고 그런 무사도 정신을 추구하는 것이 사무라이라고\n예전에 잡지에서 읽은 적이 있어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event08-05-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"실제로 사무라이를 본 적은 없지만……\n무사도를 추구하는 사람한테 동경을 품는 건\n저한테는 평범한 일인 것 같아요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event08-05-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"이브 짱한테 사무라이는 이브 짱의\n이상을 합쳐놓은 하나의 개념인 거네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event08-05-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"사무라이라는 개념……?\n큰일이다, 하나도 모르겠어……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event08-05-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"자기 자신의 이상을 추구하는 것을 가진 사람한테 동경을 느끼는 거야.\n그것이 이브 짱의 경우에는 마침 사무라이라는 존재였던 것뿐.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expression